                            <comment id="17898400" author="gharris1727" created="Thu, 14 Nov 2024 19:43:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The taskConfigs method should be changed to return an empty set of task configs if the connector is disabled, even if the consumer group load has not yet completed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
