                            <comment id="17898540" author="JIRAUSER307733" created="Fri, 15 Nov 2024 09:15:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hello &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=gharris1727&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;gharris1727&quot;&gt;gharris1727&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=frankvicky&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;frankvicky&quot;&gt;frankvicky&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thank you for creating this issue and for your efforts in resolving the problem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We wanted to point out that we have also filed a bug report for this same issue: &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-18007&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-18007&lt;/a&gt; - &apos;MirrorCheckpointConnector fails with &#8220;Timeout while loading consumer groups&#8221; after upgrading to Kafka 3.9.0&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

